docs.text: joe versus the volcano is really one of the worse movies made in very recent memory .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the strangest thing is that you would think nothing would go wrong with it .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: it has a solid cast with tom hanks & meg ryan as the lead roles .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: but you can never judge a movie by its cast . . .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: if there is one good thing about joe vs the volcano , it is that the plot is original .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: unfortunately , it is also incredibly stupid .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the movie begins with joe ( tom hanks ) going to work .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: this opening sequence is very boring and slow .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: it shows joe walking to his office .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: but on the way , he has to wait in a long line passing by strange and slightly depressing scenery with obnoxious lighting .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: a sequence like this should take 2 minutes .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: here , it takes over 5 . . .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: it is obvious that joe hates his job .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: at his office , one of his co-workers is meg ryan .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: oddly enough , she plays 3 different roles in this movie ! !
docs.label: negative

docs.text: joe leaves to go to a doctor's appointment .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: his doctor informs him that he has a " brain cloud . "
docs.label: negative

docs.text: this means that in a few months , he will die .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: so what does joe do ?
docs.label: negative

docs.text: quit his job , of course ! !
docs.label: negative

docs.text: when he arrives home , joe meets an old man named graynamore ( lloyd bridges ) .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: graynamore tells joe that in order to get some important mineral for his company from an island , the natives need someone to sacrifice to their volcano to please their fire god .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: by a startling coincidence , the boat trip to the island takes a few months .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: by the time he reaches the island , he will almost be dead from the " brain cloud " anyway , so joe agrees .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: graynamore gives joe a credit card to buy everything he needs to go on this " great adventure " .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: joe goes on a date with meg ryan , his co-worker .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the day before the boat trip , joe meets one of graynamore's daughters .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: she is also , surprise , meg ryan .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: except she looks more hippyish .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: they both have dinner and the next day , joe gets driven over to his boat .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the lady that sails the boat is another one of graynamore's daughters .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: and , wonder of wonders , she is also played by meg ryan .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: as they sail to the island , meg ryan tells joe that the natives of the island have a craving for orange soda .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: after some stupid talking scenes , they also deduce that graynamore had his doctor be the one that joe went to .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: and that the " brain cloud " thing was made up ! !
docs.label: negative

docs.text: they do plently of cheap special effects on the boat voyage .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: joe goes fishing and catches a hammerhead shark .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: this is a cheap gag that has been pulled off many times .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: but , to top it off , the shark is obviously rubber and fake ! !
docs.label: negative

docs.text: one night there is a storm .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: a cheap-looking lightning bolt strikes the boat and everything is cast overboard .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: fortunately , joe and meg ryan manage to find some of the luggage that joe brought to sail .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: by pure luck , they get to the island .
docs.label: negative

docs.label: negative

docs.text: stupid or what ?
